## **7. ERROR HANDLING**

### **Validation Errors (Before Save):**
```
Primary Services is required
Please select at least one primary industry
Geographic footprint is required
Please select at least one pricing model
```
- Display inline above save button
- Red text, icon
- Prevent save

### **Processing Errors (During Save):**
```
⚠️ Unable to save data. Please try again.
```
- Display if database save fails
- Button returns to enabled state
- Allow retry

### **Synthesis Errors (During GPT Call):**
```
⚠️ Unable to generate profile analysis. Your data has been saved.
   You can try again by clicking "Save Identity Data".
```
- Data is saved, but synthesis failed
- Allow user to retry
- Button returns to enabled state

### **Web Scrape Errors (Background):**
```
⚠️ Unable to analyze website. Profile generated from form data only.

Show in Identity Profile section
Synthesis proceeds with form data only
Not a blocking error


